version_description: This was played live in Richmond, VA on 3-10-17 for the first time. Its new so its not on any Avett Brothers albums yet. The "Bent a cough on over, cuddle and nestle" line might be wrong. Its a little hard to understand in the video.
Its a Benji Hughes song but I wanted to create the version the Avett Brothers play. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3xmRDKdLc_U.
This is the first version of this song written for chords, rather than as a tab.
The is a Townes Van Zandt Cover by Scott Avett. It's just the chords.

song_name: Head Full Of Doubt Road Full Of Promise
